'''''Star Wars: Legacy'' 0''' is the pre-release supplement of the ''[[Star Wars: Legacy]]'' comic series. It was released [[June 7]], [[2006]], and instead of a story, served as an introduction to the series. It cost twenty-five cents. An [[Star Wars: Legacy (2006) 0½|expanded issue]] was later released.

==Publisher's summary==
'''''Welcome to the beginning of a grand, new chapter in the ''Star Wars'' saga!'''''

''More than a hundred years have passed since the events in ''Return of the Jedi'' and the days of the ''The New Jedi Order''. There is a new evil gripping the galaxy, shattering a resurgent Empire and seeking to destroy the last of the Jedi. Even as their power is failing, the Jedi hold to one final hope: the last remaining heir to the Skywalker legacy''.

''It's a brave new galaxy for'' Star Wars'' fans, at once familiar and surprising&mdash;interplanetary intrigue and adventure on an epic scale; iconic heroes and villains cast in new roles and caught in surprising new situations. Everything you've loved about ''Star Wars'', but nothing you expect!''

''This special 25¢ comic sets the stage for the launch of the new ''Star Wars: Legacy'' series, which began in June 2006!''

